'''结核病'''（{{lang|en|Tuberculosis}}，又稱'''TB'''）為[[結核桿菌|結核桿菌]]感染引起的疾病。结核通常造成[[肺|肺]]部感染，也会感染身体的其他部分<ref name=WHO2015Fact/>。大多數感染者沒有症狀，此型態感染稱為{{le|潛伏結核感染|Latent tuberculosis}}。如果此時沒有適當治療，10%的潛伏感染患者會惡化為開放性結核病（Active tuberculosis），致死率為 50%。結核病的典型症狀包含慢性[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]、[[咳血|咳血]]、[[發燒|發燒]]、夜間[[潮熱|潮熱]]，以及[[減肥|體重減輕]]<ref name=Cha1998>{{cite book|title=The Chambers Dictionary.|year=1998|publisher=Allied Chambers India Ltd.|location=New Delhi|isbn=978-81-86062-25-8|pages=352|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pz2ORay2HWoC&pg=RA1-PA352}}</ref>。感染其他器官則可能導致其他症狀。<ref name=ID10>{{cite book|last=Dolin|first=[edited by] Gerald L. Mandell, John E. Bennett, Raphael|title=Mandell, Douglas, and Bennett's principles and practice of infectious diseases|year=2010|publisher=Churchill Livingstone/Elsevier|location=Philadelphia, PA|isbn=978-0-443-06839-3|pages=Chapter 250|edition=7th}}</ref>

結核病屬於[[空氣傳播疾病|空氣傳播疾病]]。意即病原體會藉由開放性結核患者咳嗽、打噴嚏，或說話過程中所產生的飛沫散佈<ref name=WHO2015Fact/><ref name=CDC2012B>{{cite web|title=Basic TB Facts|url=http://www.cdc.gov/tb/topic/basics/default.htm|website=CDC|accessdate=2016-02-11|date=2012-03-13|archive-date=2016-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206032136/http://www.cdc.gov/tb/topic/basics/default.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而潛伏性結核病患者則不會散布疾病。開放性結核常發生於[[鼠疫|鼠疫]]及[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]患者<ref name=WHO2015Fact/>，需藉由[[胸部X光|胸部X光]]、[[顯微鏡|顯微鏡檢]]，及體液培養來進行診斷。潛伏性結核病患者則可利用[[結核菌素試驗|結核菌素試驗]]或血液檢查來診斷。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Diagnostic tests: Testing for tuberculosis|url=https://www.nps.org.au/australian-prescriber/magazine/33/1/12/18|last=Konstantinos|first=Anastasios|date=2010-02-01|journal=Australian Prescriber|issue=1|doi=10.18773/austprescr.2010.005|volume=33|pages=12–18}}</ref>

預防肺結核可透過篩檢高風險者、早期診斷和治療，以及接種[[卡介苗|卡介苗]]等方法達成<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Tuberculosis Vaccines and Prevention of Infection|url=https://journals.asm.org/doi/10.1128/MMBR.00021-14|last=Hawn|first=Thomas R.|last2=Day|first2=Tracey A.|date=2014-12|journal=Microbiology and Molecular Biology Reviews|issue=4|doi=10.1128/MMBR.00021-14|volume=78|pages=650–671|language=en|issn=1092-2172|pmc=PMC4248657|pmid=25428938|last3=Scriba|first3=Thomas J.|last4=Hatherill|first4=Mark|last5=Hanekom|first5=Willem A.|last6=Evans|first6=Thomas G.|last7=Churchyard|first7=Gavin J.|last8=Kublin|first8=James G.|last9=Bekker|first9=Linda-Gail}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Harris|first1=Randall E.|title=Epidemiology of chronic disease: global perspectives|url=https://archive.org/details/epidemiologyofch0000harr|date=2013|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|location=Burlington, MA|isbn=9780763780470|page=[https://archive.org/details/epidemiologyofch0000harr/page/682 682]|ref=https://books.google.ca/books?id=KJLEIvX4wzoC&pg=PA682}}</ref><ref name=TBCon2008>{{cite book|last1=Organization|first1=World Health|title=Implementing the WHO Stop TB Strategy: a handbook for national TB control programmes|date=2008|publisher=World Health Organization|location=Geneva|isbn=9789241546676|page=179|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=EUZXFCrlUaEC&pg=PA179|access-date=2016-09-05|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216180345/https://books.google.ca/books?id=EUZXFCrlUaEC&pg=PA179|dead-url=no}}</ref>。高風險者包含生活環境中與開放性結核病患者密切接觸的人<ref name=TBCon2008/>。治療通常搭配不同的[[抗细菌药|抗生素]]組合做一段時間的治療。近年帶有[[抗生素抗藥性|抗生素抗藥性]]的結核桿菌（MDR-TB）日益增加。<ref name=WHO2015Fact/>

世界上大約有三分之一的人口患有無法傳染的潛伏性結核病<ref name=WHO2015Fact/>。全球每年大約有1%的人口新感染該病<ref name=WHO2002>{{cite web|title=Tuberculosis|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/who104/en/print.html|work=World Health Organization|year=2002|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617193438/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/who104/en/print.html|archivedate=2013-06-17}}</ref>，2014年全球有960萬名開放性結核病患者，150萬例死亡，死亡者當中有95%是來自[[發展中國家|發展中國家]]。自2000年起，全球新病例數已逐年下降<ref name=WHO2015Fact>{{cite web|title=Tuberculosis Fact sheet N°104|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs104/en/|website=WHO|accessdate=2016-02-11|date=October 2015|archive-date=2012-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120823143802/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs104/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在許多[[亚洲|亞洲]]與[[非洲|非洲]]國家，大約有80%的人肺結核檢驗結果為陽性，而在[[美國|美國]]的人口中約有5-10%的人肺結核檢驗為陽性<ref name=Robbins>{{cite book |vauthors=Kumar V, Abbas AK, Fausto N, Mitchell RN |year=2007 |title=Robbins Basic Pathology |url=https://archive.org/details/robbinsbasicpath0000unse_q0t1 |edition=8th |publisher=Saunders Elsevier |pages=[https://archive.org/details/robbinsbasicpath0000unse_q0t1/page/516 516]–522 |isbn=978-1-4160-2973-1}}</ref>。結核病在[[古代史|古代史]]中就有記載。<ref name=Lancet11>{{cite journal|last=Lawn|first=SD|author2=Zumla, AI |title=Tuberculosis|journal=Lancet|date=2011-07-02|volume=378|issue=9785|pages=57–72|pmid=21420161|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(10)62173-3}}</ref>

结核病也是一种人兽共患的传染病，可以感染包括[[人|人]]在内的不同种属的[[温血动物|温血动物]]，包括[[有蹄类|有蹄类]]、[[食肉目|食肉类]]和[[啮齿动物|啮齿动物]]等<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Problems and countermeasures in the surveillance and research of wildlife epidemics based on mammals in China|url=https://www.biodiversity-science.net/EN/10.17520/biods.2020124|last=Xiao|first=Zhishu|last2=Zhang|first2=Libiao|date=2020-05-20|journal=Biodiversity Science|issue=5|doi=10.17520/biods.2020124|volume=28|pages=566|language=en|issn=1005-0094|last3=Xu|first3=Lei|last4=Zhou|first4=Qihai|last5=Meng|first5=Xiuxiang|last6=Yan|first6=Chuan|last7=Chang|first7=Gang}}</ref>。

==臨床體徵與症狀==
[[File:Tuberculosis_symptoms.svg|thumb]]Health|author=Schiffman G|date=2009-01-15|accessdate=2016-11-21|archive-date=2009-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090516075020/http://www.emedicinehealth.com/tuberculosis/page3_em.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。許多變種的主要症狀相互重疊，而又有一些變種有其獨特（但並不一定是完全獨特）的症狀，幾個變種的症狀也可同時表現出來。]]
結核病可以在全身的任何一個部位發病，但最常發病於肺（即被稱為肺結核）。肺外結核病（即在肺以外的器官發生的結核病）可能與肺結核共同存在<ref name=ID10/>。

結核病一般的臨床體徵與症狀包括[[發熱|發熱]]、[[發冷|發冷]]、[[盜汗|盜汗]]、[[食慾不振|食慾不振]]、[[減肥|體重減輕]]以及[[疲倦|疲倦]]<ref name="ID10" />。結核病患者也可能出現明顯的{{le|杵狀指甲|Nail clubbing}}症狀<ref name="Pet2005">{{cite book|last1=Gibson|title=Evidence-Based Respiratory Medicine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208072842/http://www.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-072791605X.html|archive-date=2015-12-08|access-date=2016-11-26|url=http://www.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-072791605X.html|edition=1st|page=321|isbn=978-0-7279-1605-1|publisher=BMJ Books|date=2005|first6=Ulrich (ed.)|first1=Peter G. (ed.)|last6=Costabel|first5=Michael (ed.)|last5=Hensley|first4=Jimmy (ed.)|last4=Volmink|first3=Richard (ed.)|last3=Wood-Baker|first2=Michael (ed.)|last2=Abramson|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===肺結核===
開放性結核病最常見於肺部（占約90%的病例）<ref name=Lancet11/><ref>{{cite book|last=Behera|first=D.|title=Textbook of Pulmonary Medicine|year=2010|publisher=Jaypee Brothers Medical Publishers|location=New Delhi|isbn=978-81-8448-749-7|pages=457|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0TbJjd9eTp0C&pg=PA457|edition=2nd}}</ref>。肺結核的症狀可能包含[[胸痛|胸痛]]和長時間帶痰咳嗽，而約有25%的人可能不會表現任何症狀（即「無症狀的」）<ref name=Lancet11/>。 偶爾，患者可能小量的[[咳血|咳血]]、[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]，在極為罕見的病例中，感染可能侵蝕到[[肺動脈|肺動脈]]和{{le|雷斯莫森氏動脈瘤|Rasmussen's aneurysm}}，導致大量出血<ref name=ID10/><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Halezeroğlu|first1=S|last2=Okur|first2=E|title=Thoracic surgery for haemoptysis in the context of tuberculosis: what is the best management approach?|journal=Journal of Thoracic Disease|date=March 2014|volume=6|issue=3|pages=182–5|pmid=24624281|doi=10.3978/j.issn.2072-1439.2013.12.25}}</ref>。肺結核可能演變成慢性疾病，並導致上肺葉產生大疤痕。上肺葉比下肺葉更易受到肺結核的影響<ref name=ID10/>，但這個差別的原因目前還未明。可能的解釋為上肺葉的空氣流通較佳<ref name="Robbins" />，或其[[淋巴|淋巴]]引流能力較差<ref name=ID10/>。

===肺外結核病===
在15％至20%的開放性結核病案例中，結核桿菌感染可傳播至肺外，引起其他種類的結核病<ref>{{cite book|last=Jindal|first=editor-in-chief SK|title=Textbook of Pulmonary and Critical Care Medicine|publisher=Jaypee Brothers Medical Publishers|location=New Delhi|isbn=978-93-5025-073-0|pages=549|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EvGTw3wn-zEC&pg=PA549|year=2011}}</ref>。這些病症被歸類為「肺外結核病」。 肺外結核病常發生於存在[[免疫抑制|免疫抑制]]的個體或幼兒，50％以上患有肺結核的HIV病毒攜帶者均患有肺外結核病<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Extrapulmonary tuberculosis: an overview|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16300038|last=Golden|first=Marjorie P.|last2=Vikram|first2=Holenarasipur R.|date=2005-11-01|journal=American Family Physician|issue=9|volume=72|pages=1761–1768|issn=0002-838X|pmid=16300038}}</ref>。肺外結核病常發病於[[胸膜腔|胸膜腔]]（結核性胸膜炎）、[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]（結核性[[腦膜炎|腦膜炎]]）、[[淋巴系統|淋巴系統]]（即頸部{{le|淋巴結核|Scofula}}，又稱瘰癧）、泌尿生殖道系統（即{{le|尿殖道結核|urogenital tuberculosis}}），以及骨與筋腱（即[[博特氏病|博特氏病]]；脊柱結核性彎曲）等部位。當結核病發病於骨骼時，也被稱為「骨結核病」<ref>{{cite book|last=Kabra|first=[edited by] Vimlesh Seth, S.K.|title=Essentials of tuberculosis in children|year=2006|publisher=Jaypee Bros. Medical Publishers|location=New Delhi|isbn=978-81-8061-709-6|pages=249|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HkH0YbyBHDQC&pg=PA249|edition=3rd}}</ref>，即一種骨髓炎<ref name="Robbins" />。有時結核性膿腫破出皮膚導致結核性潰瘍<ref>{{cite book|title=Manual of Surgery|url=https://archive.org/details/manualofsurgery0000thom|year=2008|publisher=Kaplan Publishing|isbn=9781427797995|pages=[https://archive.org/details/manualofsurgery0000thom/page/75 75]}}</ref>。由周圍感染的淋巴結產生的潰瘍常表現為無痛、緩慢擴大以及看起來像水洗過的皮革的特性<ref>{{cite book|last=Burkitt|first=H. George|title=Essential Surgery: Problems, Diagnosis & Management 4th ed|year=2007|isbn=9780443103452|pages=34}}</ref>。彌散性結核病是一種更具危險性、更易擴散的結核病，也被稱為{{le|粟粒狀結核|Milliary tuberculosis}}<ref name=ID10/>，粟粒狀結核占肺外結核病例的10％<ref name=Gho2008>{{cite book|last=Ghosh|first=editors-in-chief, Thomas M. Habermann, Amit K.|title=Mayo Clinic internal medicine: concise textbook|year=2008|publisher=Mayo Clinic Scientific Press|location=Rochester, MN|isbn=978-1-4200-6749-1|pages=789|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YJtodBwNxokC&pg=PA789}}</ref>。

另外在台灣較常見的肺外結核為淋巴結核和骨結核，而結核性腦膜炎為其次，肺外結核的發生率比肺結核低<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cdc.gov.tw/professional/knowdisease.aspx?treeid=beac9c103df952c4&nowtreeid=89b930c89c1c71cf&id=FE81C4ADE2A4A38F&did=652|title=台灣衛生福利部疾病管制署-傳染病介紹-肺結核|accessdate=2016年9月12日|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121234430/http://www.cdc.gov.tw/professional/knowdisease.aspx?treeid=beac9c103df952c4&nowtreeid=89b930c89c1c71cf&id=FE81C4ADE2A4A38F&did=652|archive-date=2016年11月21日|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。而在中国大陆，以1996年至1999年上海市的流行病學研究為例，肺外结核發病案例以周围淋巴结结核为主,占38.3%,余依次为骨关节结核(19.9%)、泌尿生殖系统结核(16.7%)及肠、腹膜结核(9.1%)和脑神经结核(6.4%)。男女之比为1:1.35<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://xueshu.baidu.com/s?wd=paperuri:(d147935dcd632838cebe56fdcadb8a1d)&filter=sc_long_sign&tn=SE_xueshusource_2kduw22v&sc_vurl=http://wenku.baidu.com/view/b4863f8b3186bceb19e8bba4.html&ie=utf-8&sc_us=6562174529045101614 |title=上海市肺外结核的流行病学分析|accessdate=2016-11-21|work=xueshu.baidu.com}}</ref>。

==病因==
===分枝桿菌屬===
{{main|結核桿菌}}
[[File:Mycobacterium_tuberculosis.jpg|thumb]]下的結核桿菌]]
[[結核桿菌|結核桿菌]]是主要引起結核病的致病原，它是一個小型、[[好氧生物|好氧]]、不具活動性的細菌，屬於[[分枝桿菌屬|分枝桿菌屬]]<ref name=ID10/>。結核桿菌的生長速度與其他細菌相比非常緩慢，細胞每16至20小時才[[分裂_(生物学)|分裂]]一次，而其他細菌一般則不到半小時即分裂一次<ref>{{cite book|last=Jindal|first=editor-in-chief SK|title=Textbook of Pulmonary and Critical Care Medicine|publisher=Jaypee Brothers Medical Publishers|location=New Delhi|isbn=978-93-5025-073-0|pages=525|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rAT1bdnDakAC&pg=PA525|year=2011}}</ref>。結核桿菌還有一個特殊的雙層脂質[[細菌結構|外膜]]<ref name=Niederweis2010>{{cite journal |vauthors=Niederweis M, Danilchanka O, Huff J, Hoffmann C, Engelhardt H |title=Mycobacterial outer membranes: in search of proteins |journal=Trends in Microbiology |volume=18 |issue=3 |pages=109–16 |date=March 2010 |pmid=20060722 |pmc=2931330 |doi=10.1016/j.tim.2009.12.005 }}</ref>。細胞壁富含脂質是分枝桿菌屬特有的臨床特徵<ref>{{cite book |author=Southwick F |title=Infectious Diseases: A Clinical Short Course, 2nd ed. |publisher=McGraw-Hill Medical Publishing Division |date=2007-12-10 |pages=104, 313–4 |chapter=Chapter 4: Pulmonary Infections |isbn=0-07-147722-5}}</ref>，使用一般的[[革蘭氏染色|革蘭氏染色]]鑑定，會出現不明顯的陽性反應或無法被染上色的現象，原因就是其細胞壁中富含脂質以及{{le|黴菌酸（分枝菌酸）|Mycolic acid}}（一種脂肪酸）<ref name=Madison_2001>{{cite journal |author=Madison B |title=Application of stains in clinical microbiology |journal=Biotechnic & Histochemistry |volume=76 |issue=3 |pages=119–25 |year=2001 |pmid=11475314 |doi=10.1080/714028138}}</ref>。在自然界，結核桿菌只能生長於[[宿主|宿主]]個體的細胞中，但在實驗室中可[[In_vitro|在試管內]]培養<ref name=Parish_1999>{{cite journal |author1=Parish T. |author2=Stoker N. |title=Mycobacteria: bugs and bugbears (two steps forward and one step back) |journal=Molecular Biotechnology |volume=13 |issue=3 |pages=191–200 |year=1999| pmid=10934532 |doi = 10.1385/MB:13:3:191}}</ref>。

醫檢師可利用[[组织_(生物学)|組織]]染色法處理[[痰液|痰液]]檢體，便可用顯微鏡鑑別出結核桿菌。因為結核桿菌染色後不會被酸性溶劑沖洗掉，分類上又被稱為{{link-en|抗酸性桿菌|Acid-fast bacillus}}<ref name="Robbins" /><ref name="Madison_2001" />。目前最常用的耐酸染色法是[[齐尔-尼尔森染色|齐尔-尼尔森染色]]及{{link-en|金氏（Kinyoun）染色|Kinyoun stain}}，兩染色法在顯微鏡下所見的背景為藍色，而結核桿菌則是呈現紅色<ref name="Stain2000">{{cite book |title=Medical Laboratory Science: Theory and Practice |publisher=Tata McGraw-Hill |location=New Delhi |year=2000 |pages=473 |isbn=0-07-463223-X |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lciNs3VQPLoC&pg=PA473}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Acid-Fast Stain Protocols|url=http://www.microbelibrary.org/component/resource/laboratory-test/2870-acid-fast-stain-protocols|accessdate=2016-03-26|date=2013-08-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111001132818/http://www.microbelibrary.org/component/resource/laboratory-test/2870-acid-fast-stain-protocols|archivedate=2011年10月1日}}</ref>。另外也可使用{{link-en|金胺-若丹明（Auramine-rhodamine ）染色法|Auramine-rhodamine stain}}，並在[[螢光顯微鏡|螢光顯微鏡]]下觀察<ref name="Kommareddi_1984">{{cite journal|author1=Kommareddi S. |author2=Abramowsky C. |author3=Swinehart G. |author4=Hrabak L. |title=Nontuberculous mycobacterial infections: comparison of the fluorescent auramine-O and Ziehl-Neelsen techniques in tissue diagnosis|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_human-pathology_1984-11_15_11/page/1085 |journal=Human Pathology|volume=15|issue=11|pages=1085–1089|year=1984|pmid=6208117|doi=10.1016/S0046-8177(84)80253-1}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=van Lettow|first1=Monique|last2=Whalen|first2=Christopher|title=Nutrition and health in developing countries|year=2008|publisher=Humana Press|location=Totowa, N.J. (Richard D. Semba and Martin W. Bloem, eds.)|isbn=978-1-934115-24-4|pages=291|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RhH6uSQy7a4C&pg=PA291|edition=2nd}}</ref>。

结核分枝杆菌复合群(MTBC)包括其他四种可引起结核病的[[分枝桿菌屬|分枝桿菌屬]]的細菌：{{le|牛分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium bovis}}、{{le|非洲分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium africanum}}、{{le|卡氏分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium canetti}}及{{le|田鼠分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium microti}}<ref>{{cite journal |author=van Soolingen D. |title=A novel pathogenic taxon of the Mycobacterium tuberculosis complex, Canetti: characterization of an exceptional isolate from Africa |journal=International Journal of Systematic Bacteriology |volume=47 |issue=4 |pages=1236–45 |year=1997 |pmid=9336935 |doi=10.1099/00207713-47-4-1236 |name-list-format=vanc |display-authors=1 |last2=Hoogenboezem |first2=T. |last3=De Haas |first3=P.E.W.|last4=Hermans |first4=P.W.M. |last5=Koedam |first5=M.A. |last6=Teppema |first6=K.S. |last7=Brennan |first7=P.J.|last8=Besra |first8=G.S.|last9=Portaels |first9=F.}}</ref>。 非洲分枝桿菌分佈不廣，但卻是導致非洲結核病感染的重要因素<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mycobacterium africanum Subtype II Is Associated with Two Distinct Genotypes and Is a Major Cause of Human Tuberculosis in Kampala, Uganda|url=https://journals.asm.org/doi/10.1128/JCM.40.9.3398-3405.2002|last=Niemann|first=S.|last2=Rüsch-Gerdes|first2=S.|date=2002-09|journal=Journal of Clinical Microbiology|issue=9|doi=10.1128/JCM.40.9.3398-3405.2002|volume=40|pages=3398–3405|language=en|issn=0095-1137|pmc=PMC130701|pmid=12202584|last3=Joloba|first3=M. L.|last4=Whalen|first4=C. C.|last5=Guwatudde|first5=D.|last6=Ellner|first6=J. J.|last7=Eisenach|first7=K.|last8=Fumokong|first8=N.|last9=Johnson|first9=J. L.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Genetic Biodiversity of Mycobacterium tuberculosis Complex Strains from Patients with Pulmonary Tuberculosis in Cameroon|url=https://journals.asm.org/doi/10.1128/JCM.41.6.2547-2553.2003|last=Niobe-Eyangoh|first=Sara Ngo|last2=Kuaban|first2=Christopher|date=2003-06|journal=Journal of Clinical Microbiology|issue=6|doi=10.1128/JCM.41.6.2547-2553.2003|volume=41|pages=2547–2553|language=en|issn=0095-1137|pmc=PMC156567|pmid=12791879|last3=Sorlin|first3=Philippe|last4=Cunin|first4=Patrick|last5=Thonnon|first5=Jocelyn|last6=Sola|first6=Christophe|last7=Rastogi|first7=Nalin|last8=Vincent|first8=Veronique|last9=Gutierrez|first9=M. Cristina}}</ref>。牛分枝桿菌曾是導致結核病感染的常見因素，但因[[巴斯德消毒法|巴式消毒法]]在牛奶生產中的使用，在發達國家已幾乎不再出現牛分枝桿菌導致結核病感染的病例<ref name="Robbins" /><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Thoen C, Lobue P, de Kantor I |title=The importance of ''Mycobacterium bovis'' as a zoonosis |journal=Veterinary Microbiology |volume=112 |issue=2–4 |pages=339–45 |year=2006 |pmid=16387455 |doi=10.1016/j.vetmic.2005.11.047}}</ref>。卡式分枝桿菌較為罕見，且似乎僅出現於[[非洲之角|非洲之角（東北非洲）]]，但也有少數幾例病例出現於非洲裔移民中<ref>{{cite book|last=Acton|first=Q. Ashton|title=Mycobacterium Infections: New Insights for the Healthcare Professional|year=2011|publisher=ScholarlyEditions|isbn=978-1-4649-0122-5|pages=1968|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=g2iFfV6uEuAC&pg=PA1968}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mycobacterium canettii, the smooth variant of M. tuberculosis, isolated from a Swiss patient exposed in Africa|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9866740|last=Pfyffer|first=G. E.|last2=Auckenthaler|first2=R.|date=1998-10|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|issue=4|doi=10.3201/eid0404.980414|volume=4|pages=631–634|issn=1080-6040|pmc=2640258|pmid=9866740|last3=van Embden|first3=J. D.|last4=van Soolingen|first4=D.}}</ref>。田鼠分枝桿菌也較為罕見，且幾乎僅出現於免疫不全人群，但其[[盛行率|盛行率]]可能被嚴重低估<ref>{{cite journal|last=Panteix|first=G|author2=Gutierrez, MC |author3=Boschiroli, ML |author4=Rouviere, M |author5=Plaidy, A |author6=Pressac, D |author7=Porcheret, H |author8=Chyderiotis, G |author9=Ponsada, M |author10=Van Oortegem, K |author11=Salloum, S |author12=Cabuzel, S |author13=Bañuls, AL |author14=Van de Perre, P |author15=Godreuil, S |title=Pulmonary tuberculosis due to Mycobacterium microti: a study of six recent cases in France|journal=Journal of Medical Microbiology|date=August 2010|volume=59|issue=Pt 8|pages=984–9|pmid=20488936|doi=10.1099/jmm.0.019372-0}}</ref>

其他致病分枝桿菌屬細菌包括[[痲瘋桿菌|痲瘋桿菌]]、{{link-en|鳥分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium avium complex}}及{{link-en|堪塞斯分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium kansasii}}。後兩者被歸為{{link-en|非结核性分枝杆菌(NTM)|Nontuberculous mycobacteria}}。非结核性分枝杆菌既不能引起結核病也不能引起[[痲瘋病|痲瘋病]]，但其感染會導致相似於結核病的肺部疾病<ref name="ALA_1997">{{cite journal |title=Diagnosis and treatment of disease caused by nontuberculous mycobacteria. This official statement of the American Thoracic Society was approved by the Board of Directors, March 1997. Medical Section of the American Lung Association |journal=American Journal of Respiratory and Critical Care Medicine |volume=156 |issue=2 Pt 2 |pages=S1–25 |year=1997 |pmid = 9279284 |author=American Thoracic Society |doi=10.1164/ajrccm.156.2.atsstatement }}</ref>。

===危險因子===
有許多因子會讓人更容易罹患肺結核。目前全球最重要的一項危險因子是[[HIV|HIV]]病毒；在罹患肺結核的病人中，有13%是HIV病毒感染的患者<ref name=WHO2011>{{cite web|title=The sixteenth global report on tuberculosis|author=World Health Organization|url=http://www.who.int/tb/publications/global_report/2011/gtbr11_executive_summary.pdf|year=2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120906223650/http://www.who.int/tb/publications/global_report/2011/gtbr11_executive_summary.pdf|archivedate=2012-09-06}}</ref>。 該問題在[[撒哈拉以南非洲|漠南非洲]]尤其顯著，因為這個區域愛滋病罹患率相當高<ref>{{cite web|author=World Health Organization|url=http://www.who.int/tb/publications/global_report/en/index.html|title=Global tuberculosis control–surveillance, planning, financing WHO Report 2006|accessdate=2006-10-13|archive-date=2006-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061212123736/http://www.who.int/tb/publications/global_report/en/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{cite journal|last=Chaisson|first=RE|author2=Martinson, NA |title=Tuberculosis in Africa—combating an HIV-driven crisis|journal=The New England Journal of Medicine|date=2008-03-13|volume=358|issue=11|pages=1089–92|pmid=18337598|doi=10.1056/NEJMp0800809}}</ref>。 未感染HIV的肺結核患者中，有約5～10%日後發展為開放性肺結核； 相比之下，同時感染HIV的肺結核患者日後有30％發展為開放性肺結核<ref name=Pet2005/>。肺結核與擁擠環境、[[營養不良|營養不良]]相關，這些特性使其成為{{le|貧窮病|disease of proverty}}之一<ref name=Lancet11/>。 其他高風險因子則包含注射毒品、人口聚集場所居民及工作人員（如收容所及監獄）、醫療衛生較差區域、某些特定種族、與病患長期接觸的孩童，以及醫療照護人員等等<ref name=Griffith_1996>{{cite journal |vauthors=Griffith D, Kerr C | title=Tuberculosis: disease of the past, disease of the present | journal=Journal of Perianesthesia Nursing | volume=11 | issue=4 | pages=240–5 | year=1996 | pmid=8964016 | doi=10.1016/S1089-9472(96)80023-2 }}</ref>。慢性肺部疾病是另一種重要的危險因子。{{link-en|矽肺症|Silicosis}}提高了大約30倍的風險<ref name=":2" />。[[香煙|吸煙者]]相於沒有吸煙的族群，有大約兩倍罹患肺結核的風險<ref>{{cite journal|last=van Zyl Smit|first=RN|author2=Pai, M |author3=Yew, WW |author4=Leung, CC |author5=Zumla, A |author6=Bateman, ED |author7=Dheda, K |title=Global lung health: the colliding epidemics of tuberculosis, tobacco smoking, HIV and COPD| journal=European Respiratory Journal |date=January 2010|volume=35|issue=1|pages=27–33|pmid=20044459|quote=These analyses indicate that smokers are almost twice as likely to be infected with TB and to progress to active disease (RR of about 1.5 for latent TB infection (LTBI) and RR of ∼2.0 for TB disease). Smokers are also twice as likely to die from TB (RR of about 2.0 for TB mortality), but data are difficult to interpret because of heterogeneity in the results across studies.|doi=10.1183/09031936.00072909}}</ref>。另外還有一些疾病也會提高肺結核的風險，包含[[酗酒|酗酒]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]] (提高約3倍的患病機率) <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Convergence of the tuberculosis and diabetes epidemics: renewal of old acquaintances|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17638190|last=Restrepo|first=Blanca I.|date=2007-08-15|journal=Clinical Infectious Diseases: An Official Publication of the Infectious Diseases Society of America|issue=4|doi=10.1086/519939|volume=45|pages=436–438|issn=1537-6591|pmc=2900315|pmid=17638190}}</ref>。某些藥物也逐漸成為重要的風險因子，尤其是在[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]。例如[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]] 和 {{link-en|Infliximab|Infliximab}} (一種抗αTNF的單株抗體)。{{link-en|遺傳易感性|Genetic susceptibility}} 也是危險因子之一，然而其重要性目前仍未確立<ref name="Lancet11" /><ref>{{cite journal|last=Möller|first=M|author2=Hoal, EG |title=Current findings, challenges and novel approaches in human genetic susceptibility to tuberculosis|journal=Tuberculosis |date=March 2010|volume=90|issue=2|pages=71–83|pmid=20206579|doi=10.1016/j.tube.2010.02.002}}</ref>。

